  3. the total amount paid by Lalit, Giri and Hari was Rs. 100 more than the total amount paid by all the persons who ordered Arepas and Marzipan.

  4. Kiran, who paid more than Rs. 650, was the only person who ordered Poutine, while Giri was sitting two places to the left of Ajay.

  5. Rendang is priced Rs. 450 but it was not ordered by either Giri or Manan.
